Don't bug out! Cicada season is approaching in many states, so @marascampo and I did a quick Q&A with entomologist, Mike Deutsch ⬇️ 

➡️ How often do cicadas appear? 

➡️ How long are cicadas around for?

➡️ Are cicadas dangerous? 

➡️ Why do cicadas make so much noise!?

➡️ Is there anything I can do to repel cicadas? 

For more on this topic, plus travel + safety tips from @thepointsguy, be sure to watch #TheDrOzShow tomorrow. 
.

Breaking News: President Biden just announced all adults will be eligible on April 19 for the vaccine—nearly two weeks ahead of schedule. We talked to the @u.s.surgeongeneral about this, and his hopes for the #wecandothis campaign to end vaccine hesitancy.

We’ll have more with Dr. Murthy tomorrow on #TheDrOzShow. Be sure to tune in.

Let me know if you plan on adding this to your Easter menu in the comments. ⬇️ 

Grab the recipe on my Story or on doctoroz.com
